examples.en: These considerations only slightly palliate his conduct.
My mind is tossed by various considerations. (J. MacDonald)
The children have been taught to rise above selfish considerations.
All other considerations had to be subordinated to the needs of the family.
My wishes didn't figure among his considerations.
Economic considerations forced her to delay her education.
The financial considerations are laid out in a booklet called 'How to Borrow Money'.
